  StyleBox[
   RowBox[{"Z", "Z", "Z"}], "TI"]], "InlineFormula",
  FontSize->0.9 Inherited,ExpressionUUID->
  "45f62205-40db-4aba-b123-625258ce2ab4"],
 ", the conserved parity that binds the three ",
